#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1520
msgid "Default: 0"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: 0"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:561
msgid "Different types of calculation are available:"
msgstr "Dostupni su različiti tipovi izračunavanja:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:563
msgid ""
"0 --- Linear (N * *k* x 3) distance matrix: for each input point, reports "
"the distance to each of the *k* nearest target points. The output matrix "
"consists of up to *k* rows per input point, and each row has three columns: "
"*InputID*, *TargetID* and *Distance*."
msgstr ""
"0 --- Linearna (N * *k* x 3) matrica rastojanja: za svaku ulaznu tačku "
"prijavljuje rastojanje do svake od *k* najbližih ciljnih tačaka. Izlazna "
"matrica sastoji se od najviše *k* redova po ulaznoj tački, a svaki red ima "
"tri kolone: *InputID*, *TargetID* i *Distance*."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:569
msgid "1 --- Standard (N x T) distance matrix"
msgstr "1 --- Standardna (N x T) matrica rastojanja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:570
msgid ""
"2 --- Summary distance matrix (mean, std. dev., min, max): for each input "
"point, reports statistics on the distances to its target points."
msgstr ""
"2 --- Zbirna matrica rastojanja (srednja vrednost, std. dev., min, maks): za"
" svaku ulaznu tačku prijavljuje statistiku rastojanja do njenih ciljnih "
"tačaka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:573
msgid "**Use only the nearest (k) target points**"
msgstr "**Koristi samo najbližih (k) ciljnih tačaka**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:574
msgid "``NEAREST_POINTS``"
msgstr "``NEAREST_POINTS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:578
msgid ""
"You can choose to calculate the distance to all the points in the target "
"layer (*0*) or limit to a number (*k*) of closest features."
msgstr ""
"Možete izabrati da se rastojanje izračuna do svih tačaka u ciljnom sloju "
"(*0*) ili da se ograniči na određeni broj (*k*) najbližih objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:582
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:605
msgid "**Distance matrix**"
msgstr "**Matrica rastojanja**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:587
msgid ""
"Specification of the output vector layer. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Specifikacija izlaznog vektorskog sloja. :ref:`Jedno od "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:608
msgid ""
"Point (or MultiPoint for the \"Linear (N * *k* x 3)\" case) vector layer "
"containing the distance calculation for each input feature. Its features and"
" attribute table depend on the selected output matrix type."
msgstr ""
"Tačkasti (ili MultiPoint u slučaju \"Linearna (N * *k* x 3)\") vektorski "
"sloj sa izračunatim rastojanjem za svaki ulazni objekat. Njegovi objekti i "
"atributska tabela zavise od izabranog tipa izlazne matrice."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:617
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:distancematrix``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:distancematrix``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:627
msgid "Distance to nearest hub (line to hub)"
msgstr "Rastojanje do najbližeg čvorišta (linija do čvorišta)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:628
msgid ""
"Creates lines that join each feature of an input vector to the nearest "
"feature in a destination layer. Distances are calculated based on the "
":ref:`center <qgispointonsurface>` of each feature."
msgstr ""
"Pravi linije koje spajaju svaki objekat ulaznog vektorskog sloja sa "
"najbližim objektom u odredišnom sloju. Rastojanja se izračunavaju na osnovu "
":ref:`centra <qgispointonsurface>` svakog objekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:637
msgid "Display the nearest hub for the red input features"
msgstr "Prikaz najbližeg čvorišta za crvene ulazne objekte"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:639
msgid ":ref:`qgisdistancetonearesthubpoints`, :ref:`qgisjoinbynearest`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdistancetonearesthubpoints`, :ref:`qgisjoinbynearest`"

