msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:distancetonearesthublinetohub``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:725
msgid "Distance to nearest hub (points)"
msgstr "Rastojanje do najbližeg čvorišta (tačke)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:726
msgid ""
"Creates a point layer representing the :ref:`center <qgispointonsurface>` of"
" the input features with the addition of two fields containing the "
"identifier of the nearest feature (based on its center point) and the "
"distance between the points."
msgstr ""
"Pravi tačkasti sloj koji predstavlja :ref:`centar <qgispointonsurface>` "
"ulaznih objekata, uz dodatak dva polja koja sadrže identifikator najbližeg "
"objekta (na osnovu njegove središnje tačke) i rastojanje između tačaka."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:732
msgid ":ref:`qgisdistancetonearesthublinetohub`, :ref:`qgisjoinbynearest`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdistancetonearesthublinetohub`, :ref:`qgisjoinbynearest`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:779
msgid ""
"Specify the output point vector layer with the nearest hub. :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Zadajte izlazni tačkasti vektorski sloj sa najbližim čvorištem. :ref:`Jedno "
"od <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:801
msgid ""
"Point vector layer representing the center of the source features with their"
" attributes, the identifier of their closest feature and the calculated "
"distance."
msgstr ""
"Tačkasti vektorski sloj koji predstavlja centar izvornih objekata sa "
"njihovim atributima, identifikatorom njima najbližeg objekta i izračunatim "
"rastojanjem."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:808
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``qgis:distancetonearesthubpoints``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``qgis:distancetonearesthubpoints``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:818
msgid "Join by lines (hub lines)"
msgstr "Spajanje linijama (linije čvorišta)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:819
msgid ""
"Creates hub and spoke diagrams by connecting lines from points on the Spoke "
"layer to matching points in the Hub layer."
msgstr ""
"Pravi dijagrame tipa čvorište-krak povezujući linijama tačke iz sloja "
"krakova sa odgovarajućim tačkama u sloju čvorišta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:822
msgid ""
"Determination of which hub goes with each point is based on a match between "
"the Hub ID field on the hub points and the Spoke ID field on the spoke "
"points."
msgstr ""
"Koje čvorište pripada kojoj tački određuje se poklapanjem polja ID čvorišta "
"na tačkama čvorišta i polja ID kraka na tačkama krakova."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:826
msgid ""
"If input layers are not point layers, a point on the surface of the "
"geometries will be taken as the connecting location."
msgstr ""
"Ako ulazni slojevi nisu tačkasti, kao mesto povezivanja uzima se tačka na "
"površini geometrija."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:829
msgid ""
"Optionally, geodesic lines can be created, which represent the shortest path"
" on the surface of an ellipsoid. When geodesic mode is used, it is possible "
"to split the created lines at the antimeridian (±180 degrees longitude), "
"which can improve rendering of the lines. Additionally, the distance between"
" vertices can be specified. A smaller distance results in a denser, more "
"accurate line."
msgstr ""
"Opciono se mogu praviti geodetske linije, koje predstavljaju najkraći put po"
" površini elipsoida. Kada se koristi geodetski režim, napravljene linije "
"mogu se deliti na antimeridijanu (±180 stepeni geografske dužine), što može "
"poboljšati iscrtavanje linija. Dodatno se može zadati rastojanje između "
"temena. Manje rastojanje daje gušću i precizniju liniju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:838
msgid ""
"This algorithm drops existing primary keys or FID values and regenerates "
"them in output layers."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam uklanja postojeće primarne ključeve ili FID vrednosti i "
"ponovo ih generiše u izlaznim slojevima."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:843
msgid "Join points based on a common field / attribute"
msgstr "Spajanje tačaka na osnovu zajedničkog polja / atributa"

