#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:965
msgid "K-means clustering"
msgstr "K-means klasterovanje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:966
msgid ""
"Calculates the 2D distance based k-means cluster number for each input "
"feature."
msgstr ""
"Izračunava broj k-means klastera za svaki ulazni objekat na osnovu 2D "
"rastojanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:969
msgid ""
"K-means clustering aims to partition the features into k clusters in which "
"each feature belongs to the cluster with the nearest mean. The mean point is"
" represented by the barycenter of the clustered features."
msgstr ""
"K-means klasterovanje ima za cilj da podeli objekte u k klastera u kojima "
"svaki objekat pripada klasteru sa najbližom srednjom vrednošću. Srednju "
"tačku predstavlja baricentar klasterovanih objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:974
msgid ""
"If input geometries are lines or polygons, the clustering is based on the "
"centroid of the feature."
msgstr ""
"Ako su ulazne geometrije linije ili poligoni, klasterovanje se zasniva na "
"centroidu objekta."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:980
msgid "A five class point clusters"
msgstr "Klasteri tačaka u pet klasa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:982
msgid ":ref:`qgisdbscanclustering`, :ref:`qgisstdbscanclustering`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgisdbscanclustering`, :ref:`qgisstdbscanclustering`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1001
msgid "``CLUSTERS``"
msgstr "``CLUSTERS``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1005
msgid "Number of clusters to create with the features"
msgstr "Broj klastera koji se formira od objekata"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1006
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1516
msgid "**Method**"
msgstr "**Metod**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1007
