msgid "``METHOD``"
msgstr "``METHOD``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1011
msgid "Initial centers selection method. Possible values are:"
msgstr "Metod izbora početnih centara. Moguće vrednosti su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1014
msgid ""
"0 --- Farthest points: the initial centers are selected as the farthest "
"points from each other."
msgstr ""
"0 --- Najudaljenije tačke: za početne centre biraju se tačke koje su "
"najudaljenije jedna od druge."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1015
msgid ""
"1 --- K-means++: The first center is selected uniformly at random from the "
"set of input features. Subsequent centers are chosen based on a weighted "
"probability distribution that favors features farther from existing centers."
" This ensures that the initial centers are well-dispersed, reducing the "
"likelihood of poor clustering and improving the algorithm's performance."
msgstr ""
"1 --- K-means++: Prvi centar bira se uniformno slučajno iz skupa ulaznih "
"objekata. Naredni centri biraju se na osnovu težinske raspodele verovatnoće "
"koja daje prednost objektima udaljenijim od postojećih centara. Time se "
"obezbeđuje dobra raspoređenost početnih centara, smanjuje verovatnoća lošeg "
"klasterovanja i poboljšavaju performanse algoritma."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1020
msgid ""
"*References: Arthur, David & Vassilvitskii, Sergei. (2007). K-Means++: The "
"Advantages of Careful Seeding. Proc. of the Annu. ACM-SIAM Symp. on Discrete"
" Algorithms. 8.*"
msgstr ""
"*Literatura: Arthur, David & Vassilvitskii, Sergei. (2007). K-Means++: The "
"Advantages of Careful Seeding. Proc. of the Annu. ACM-SIAM Symp. on Discrete"
" Algorithms. 8.*"

