#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1380
msgid ""
"Calculates the area and percentage cover by which features from an input "
"layer are overlapped by features from a selection of overlay layers."
msgstr ""
"Izračunava površinu i procenat pokrivenosti kojom objekti iz ulaznog sloja "
"bivaju preklopljeni objektima iz izabranih slojeva za preklapanje."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1384
msgid ""
"New attributes are added to the output layer reporting the total area of "
"overlap and percentage of the input feature overlapped by each of the "
"selected overlay layers."
msgstr ""
"U izlazni sloj dodaju se novi atributi koji prijavljuju ukupnu površinu "
"preklapanja i procenat ulaznog objekta preklopljen svakim od izabranih "
"slojeva za preklapanje."

