msgid "Default: Not set"
msgstr "Podrazumevano: Nije postavljeno"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1444
msgid ""
"If provided, the input geometries are snapped to a grid of the given size, "
"and the result vertices are computed on that same grid."
msgstr ""
"Ako se zada, ulazne geometrije se prilepljuju na mrežu date veličine, a "
"temena rezultata izračunavaju se na toj istoj mreži."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1462
msgid ""
"The output layer with additional fields reporting the overlap (in map units "
"and percentage) of the input feature overlapped by each of the selected "
"layers."
msgstr ""
"Izlazni sloj sa dodatnim poljima koja prijavljuju preklapanje (u jedinicama "
"karte i procentima) ulaznog objekta sa svakim od izabranih slojeva."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1469
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:calculatevectoroverlaps``"
msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:calculatevectoroverlaps``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1479
msgid "Shortest line between features"
msgstr "Najkraća linija između objekata"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1481
msgid ""
"Creates a line layer as the shortest line between the source and the "
"destination layer. By default only the first nearest feature of the "
"destination layer is taken into account. The n-nearest neighboring features "
"number can be specified. If a maximum distance is specified, then only "
"features which are closer than this distance will be considered."
msgstr ""
"Pravi linijski sloj kao najkraću liniju između izvornog i odredišnog sloja. "
"Podrazumevano se uzima u obzir samo prvi najbliži objekat odredišnog sloja. "
"Može se zadati broj n najbližih susednih objekata. Ako se zada najveće "
"rastojanje, uzimaju se u obzir samo objekti bliži od tog rastojanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1484
msgid ""
"The output features will contain all the source layer attributes, all the "
"attributes from the n-nearest feature and the additional field of the "
"distance."
msgstr ""
"Izlazni objekti sadržaće sve atribute izvornog sloja, sve atribute n "
"najbližeg objekta i dodatno polje sa rastojanjem."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1486
msgid ""
"This algorithm uses purely Cartesian calculations for distance, and does not"
" consider geodetic or ellipsoid properties when determining feature "
"proximity. The measurement and output coordinate system is based on the "
"coordinate system of the source layer."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj algoritam koristi isključivo Dekartova izračunavanja rastojanja i ne "
"uzima u obzir geodetska svojstva ni svojstva elipsoida pri određivanju "
"blizine objekata. Koordinatni sistem merenja i izlaza zasnovan je na "
"koordinatnom sistemu izvornog sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1494
msgid "Shortest line from point features to lines"
msgstr "Najkraća linija od tačkastih objekata do linija"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1508
msgid "**Source layer**"
msgstr "**Izvorni sloj**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1509
msgid "``SOURCE``"
msgstr "``SOURCE``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1511
msgid "Origin layer for which to search for nearest neighbors"
msgstr "Polazni sloj za koji se traže najbliži susedi"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1512
msgid "**Destination layer**"
msgstr "**Odredišni sloj**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1513
msgid "``DESTINATION``"
msgstr "``DESTINATION``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1515
msgid "Target Layer in which to search for nearest neighbors"
msgstr "Ciljni sloj u kome se traže najbliži susedi"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectoranalysis.rst:1521
